whose books sell a lot...
I'll try a little harder.

rows.label: tlk01001004_msg0101

A floating island... gently...
carrying people and dreams
across the Cloud Sea...

rows.label: tlk01001004_msg0102
rows.name:
This kind of question wasn't
on the theological school's
exam. It's challenging.

rows.label: tlk01001004_msg0202
rows.name:
What if I became an old man...? I've
never thought about that before.

rows.label: tlk01001004_msg0203
rows.name:
I'm raising a rescued Kapiba as if
it were my own child, and I've
learned that parents worry a lot.

rows.label: tlk01001004_msg0204
rows.name:
Sometimes Auntie Correl's worrying
was annoying... but from now on,
I have to be grateful.
